name: fuzzysearch
description: Implements fuzzy searching on an input field
type: (node: HTMLInputElement, searchOptions: { data: Item[]; key?: string; limit?: number; }) => { destroy(): void; }

params.name: searchOptions
params.type: { data: Item[]; key?: string; limit?: number; }
params.description:
search options where `data` is an array of objects or strings to search
through, `key` is the key to search on if `data` is an array of objects,
and `limit` is the maximum number of results to return
